      "date": "2012-02-28 12:22:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/dab8c526-6204-11e1-b462-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
